item.dc:creator: @Wet_Dreamss Wet Dreamss
item.description:
@Wet_Dreamss wrote:

ultimatepkvillage:

^^wrong, she needs to change the ip in the client folder under one of these text files client.java, Egui.java or gui.java, launch.java and search for server until you find an ip then change it to 127.0.0.1-(This is for you to login) and compile. Then reload client and you should be able to login.

Lol. It’s not online means multiple things btw. I didn’t feel like giving an idiotic explanation to an idiot. A first grader should know that.
